ZH: 我是一名大学生。
EN: I am a college student.

ZH: 大学生要努力学习。
EN: College students need to study hard.

ZH: 我的弟弟马上要成为一名大学生了。
EN: My younger brother will soon become a college student.

ZH: 大学生应该广泛参加社会实践活动。
EN: College students should actively participate in social practice activities.

ZH: 这是一所理工科大学的校区。
EN: This is a campus of a university specializing in science and technology.

ZH: 大学生是社会的希望。
EN: College students are the hope of society.

ZH: 大学生应该培养良好的学习习惯。
EN: College students should cultivate good study habits.

ZH: 我每天都见到很多大学生。
EN: I see many college students every day.

ZH: 作为一名大学生，我有很多自由时间。
EN: As a college student, I have a lot of free time.

ZH: 大学生应该注重身心健康。
EN: College students should pay attention to their physical and mental health.

ZH: 大学生应该积极参与社团活动。
EN: College students should actively participate in club activities.

ZH: 作为大学生，我要为社会做出贡献。
EN: As a college student, I want to contribute to society.

ZH: 大学生在学校有很多机会锻炼自己的实践能力。
EN: College students have many opportunities to enhance their practical abilities in school.

ZH: 每年都有很多大学生毕业找工作。
EN: Many college students graduate and look for jobs every year.

ZH: 大学生应该广泛涉猎不同领域的知识。
EN: College students should have a broad knowledge base in different fields.

ZH: 这所大学有很多国际交流项目给大学生参加。
EN: This university has many international exchange programs for college students.

ZH: 大学生是社会变革的中坚力量。
EN: College students are the backbone of social change.

ZH: 作为一名大学生，我要追求自己的梦想。
EN: As a college student, I want to pursue my dreams.

ZH: 大学生应该积极参与公益活动。
EN: College students should actively participate in public welfare activities.

ZH: 大学生应该培养团队合作精神。
EN: College students should cultivate a spirit of teamwork.
